# TIMES_SHOP rules

## Project context
- TIMES_SHOP = customer-facing web store (separate repo from TIMES_POS)
- Backend = same Supabase project as TIMES_POS — never create a new database
- Product catalog syncs from TikTok Shop API via POS Edge Functions (not from browser)

## Required reading before any feature work
1. `docs/times-shop-handoff/SHOP_REQUIREMENTS.md`
2. `docs/times-shop-handoff/BACKEND_CONTRACT.md`
3. `docs/times-shop-handoff/SECURITY.md`
4. `docs/times-shop-handoff/UI_GUIDE.md`

## Hard rules (security)
- NEVER query `products`, `sale_orders`, `sale_order_items` directly from the shop client
- NEVER use service_role key in frontend
- NEVER call `tiktok-products-search` or other POS/TikTok Edge Functions from the shop
- NEVER expose cost_price, supplier data, or other shops' orders
- NEVER copy or import from TIMES_POS `main.jsx` or POS-only components
- ALL catalog/checkout APIs go through `shop-*` Edge Functions per BACKEND_CONTRACT
- Re-validate cart server-side before placing orders — never trust client prices

## Auth
- Customers get `app_role: customer` in app_metadata (set by backend trigger)
- Staff roles (admin/super_admin) may access `/admin` routes only with role check
- Use anon key + customer JWT only

## API
- If backend not deployed yet: mock responses matching BACKEND_CONTRACT exactly
- Toggle via `VITE_USE_MOCK_API=true`
- Do not invent API shapes outside the contract

## UI
- Thai language primary
- Mobile-first, cream + coral tokens from UI_GUIDE
- Min touch target 44px
- Copy money formatting pattern from POS `money.js` — do not duplicate POS UI shell

## Backend changes
- Supabase migrations and new Edge Functions belong in TIMES_POS repo — not here
- If an API is missing, add a TODO and use mock — do not create migrations in TIMES_SHOP

## Order flow
- Order flow: web orders use TikTok stock for catalog; POS still cuts POS stock on confirm
- Payment slips: admin manual review in `/admin` — no paid OCR services
- Auth: disable Supabase Confirm email — checkout without email verification
